--- Notice ---

The development of this tool or myself are in no way involved with Gandi.net.

--- Requirements ---

- Python (>= 2.7 && < 3.0)
- Python xmlrpclib, getopt, os, ConfigParser, urllib2


--- Gandi details ---

API Key (Apply here: https://www.gandi.net/admin/api_key)

--- Usage ---

gandi-dns.py --domain=<domain>.<tld> --record=<record>

